---
title: Spiced Honey Chicken with Roasted Pumpkin & Rainbow Slaw
description: The classic combination of honey and spice never goes amiss. We love the way these flavours caramelise in the
pan. The chicken breast packs a fantastic flavour, remaining moist as it cooks and complements the serving of delicious, sweet roasted pumpkin and creamy slaw.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
